<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank you for ordering through Jungle, <%= @user.try(:first_name) %>.</h1>
    <p>
      Thank you for making a purchase at Jungle!
      You can log in to our site with your username: 
      <%= @user.try(:email) %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      The total cost for your order, <%= @order.id %>, is <%= @order.total %>
      You ordered the following items:
      <% @order.line_items.each do |item| %>
      <%= item.quantity %> <%= item.product.name %>
      Price per item: <%= item.product.price %>
      <% end %>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for your purchase and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>